##
## Upstream tests to disable
##
## When adding a new filter to this list, please include a short description of
## why the filter is required and create an associated tracking issue.
##

# These tests fail because we disable prerender
-All/PrerenderHostRegistryLimitGroupTest.*
-PrerenderHandleImplTest.CallbackCalledOnFailure
-PrerenderHandleImplTest.OnResponseHeadersReceived

# These tests fail because we override FileSystemAccessHandleBase::DoMove to
# only allow moving temp files.
-All/FileSystemAccessFileHandleImplMoveWriteModeTest.RequestsCorrectPermissions/*
-All/FileSystemAccessFileHandleImplRenameWriteModeTest.RequestsCorrectPermissions/*
-FileSystemAccessFileHandleImplMoveTest.HasDestWriteAccess
-FileSystemAccessFileHandleImplMoveTest.NoDestWriteAccess
-FileSystemAccessFileHandleImplRenameTest.HasWriteAccess

# These tests fail because we disable the client hints that the tests check.
-ClientHintsTest.AddNavigationRequestClientHintsHeaders_MainFrame
-ClientHintsTest.AddNavigationRequestClientHintsHeaders_Subframe
-ClientHintsTest.AddPrefetchNavigationRequestClientHintsHeaders
-ClientHintsTest.GetCriticalHintsMissingStatus
-ClientHintsTest.GetEnabledClientHintsSubframeNotAllowed
-ClientHintsTest.IntegrationTestsOnParseLookUp

# These tests fail because we disable Prefetch/Preload
-PrefetchContainerXClientDataTests/PrefetchContainerXClientDataHeaderTest.AddHeaderForEligibleRedirectUrlOnlyWhenNotInIncognito/0
-PrefetchContainerXClientDataTests/PrefetchContainerXClientDataHeaderTest.AddHeaderForEligibleUrlOnlyWhenNotInIncognito/0
-PrefetchServiceEventTest.*

# Intermittent Mojo data pipe race: response_body().ReadData() returns 0 bytes
# after RunUntilComplete() because data hasn't been flushed through the pipe yet.
# Variant /1 is stable upstream (0.0% flake rate) so it is not filtered.
# https://github.com/brave/brave-browser/issues/52657
-WebUIURLLoaderFactoryTest.RangeRequest/0
-WebUIURLLoaderFactoryTest.RangeRequest/2
-WebUIURLLoaderFactoryTest.RangeRequest/3
-WebUIURLLoaderFactoryTest.RangeRequest/4

